    "body": "**Checkpoint**\n\nOverall disk space\n```\n427G\t/data/besu/database\n1.2G\t/data/besu/caches\n0\t\t/data/besu/fastsync\n429G\t/data/besu\n```\n\nStorage by column family\n```\nBLOCKCHAIN: 314GB 101MB 781KB 512B\nACCOUNT_INFO_STATE: 44MB 846KB 905B\nCODE_STORAGE: 8GB 715MB 115KB 599B\nACCOUNT_STORAGE_STORAGE: 151MB 360KB 711B\nTRIE_BRANCH_STORAGE: 97GB 556MB 411KB 754B\nTRIE_LOG_STORAGE: 902MB 396KB 6B\n```\n\n**Snapsync**\nOverall disk space\n```\n667G\t/data/besu/database\n3.8G\t/data/besu/caches\n0\t\t/data/besu/fastsync\n671G\t/data/besu/\n```\nStorage by column family\n```\nBLOCKCHAIN: 557GB 543MB 320KB 389B\nACCOUNT_INFO_STATE: 18MB 70KB 223B\nCODE_STORAGE: 8GB 674MB 305KB 848B\nACCOUNT_STORAGE_STORAGE: 38MB 812KB 224B\nTRIE_BRANCH_STORAGE: 96GB 352MB 24KB 363B\nTRIE_LOG_STORAGE: 299MB 523KB 242B\n```",
